snippet.textDisplay: THEIR VOCALS! Legit, they are really singing, I can't believe it. I can barely hear their pre-recorded voices because of how hard they try to sing and how hard they try to not lipsync. Not many groups do this and I know BTS have been doing it for a long time but I still can't get over it! All of them have improved so much in their singing. And their choreography is, wahhh!!!! No words to express this beautiful and powerful performance. It has everything! They just keep getting better and better! And I can't write this comment without mentioning Jungkook's vocals! During his high notes thooo, frick! Our main vocal just killed me right there! I was so surprised. My mouth went wide open. He definitely worked so hard on this despite probably how tired he was. He didn't lipsync, I can tell ya that. I barely heard his pre-recorded voice. His vocals has jUnGsHoOk me once again! That's our main vocal! Proud of all of them!!! I will always keep ON with BTS! Keep going ON, BTS! It is not the end! ARMYs will proudly be cheering you on! Borahae💜 BTS Hwaiting!💪
